dawn of the dragon racers is a 2014 computer-animated short film by dreamworks animation and directed by elaine bogan and john sanford .   based on the film series of the same name .   it was directed by john sanford and elaine bogan , and it features the voices of jay baruchel and america ferrera along with the cast from the television series .   in the short , a hunt for a lost sheep turns into a competition between hiccup and his friends for the first title of dragon racing champion of berk .